    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and double VANOS. This unit delivers exceptional throttle response and linear power through a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a 3.62 limited-slip differential. Crucial platform maintenance has been addressed, including subframe reinforcement and rod bearing replacement, ensuring structural integrity under high lateral loads. The suspension remains tight with refreshed bushings, and the cooling system has been overhauled to manage thermal loads during spirited use. While the exterior shows honest wear consistent with a well-loved driver, the powertrain remains robust with consistent compression across all cylinders.",
      "price": 32500.0,
