    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and daily reliability. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, showing only minor road wear and small stone chips consistent with careful ownership. Inside, you\u2019ll find a smoke-free cabin featuring supple leather seating and a fully functional suite of modern technology, from the intuitive infotainment system to the crisp premium audio. Mechanically, this car is in robust health; it has been serviced at strict intervals, with a comprehensive log of recent oil changes, fluid flushes, and a recent brake inspection. The engine pulls smoothly and the transmission shifts seamlessly, providing a confident, quiet driving experience on both city streets and highways. The tires have significant tread remaining, and the suspension remains tight and responsive. This is a turn-key opportunity for a buyer seeking a dependable, high-quality vehicle that has been treated with respect. Includes two sets of keys, all-weather floor mats, and original owner manuals.",
