      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It's in really solid shape and has been super reliable for all my daily commutes. It\u2019s been well-loved and is ready for its next adventure with someone new! It handles beautifully and still looks great\u2014perfect for someone who wants a dependable ride without the brand-new price tag. Come check it out and take it for a spin!",
