    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a prime example of high-revving atmospheric engineering, powered by the iconic S65 4.0L V8. The powertrain delivers peak torque with exceptional linearity, mated to a 7-speed M-DCT dual-clutch gearbox that ensures seamless gear transitions. The chassis features a sophisticated aluminum subframe and a five-link rear suspension, maintaining excellent kinematic integrity. Crucially, the rod bearings and throttle actuators\u2014common points of concern\u2014have been addressed, ensuring the internal reciprocating assembly is robust. While the exterior shows honest wear typical of a well-loved driver's car, the mechanical state is dialed-in, featuring a functional M Variable Differential Lock and fade-resistant compound rotors.",
